window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>Who is looping? Who is changing history?</i></p> <p>As Magnus has said, \"Ormr is after the crown, I need to get there first,\" but who is twisting time and causing the mess?</p> <p>Kaitlyn and Magnus and their family are in 13th century Scotland, they're trying to stick together, attempting to keep their memories intact while their timeline crumbles around them.</p> <p>With new time travel twists and turns, the next book in Mr and Mrs Campbell's history promises excitement and more more more adventure, with contemporary scenes and historical flourishes—book 16, <i>Only a Breath Away</i>.</p>"; 
